## ğŸ§  Summary

| Concept              | Description                         |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| JSX                  | JavaScript + HTML                   |
| Functional Component | Function that returns JSX           |
| Props                | Data passed to components           |
| One Parent Element   | JSX must return one wrapper element |

